flowchart TD
  A[User opens /tasks/:taskId] --> B[Route parses tab and history filters]
  B --> C[Task detail client requests /tasks/:id/detail]
  C --> D{Detail projection available?}
  D -->|Yes| E[Render summary, activity timeline, telemetry state from detail payload]
  D -->|No 404| F[Fallback to /tasks/:id + /history + /observability-summary]
  E --> G[User adjusts event type or date filters]
  F --> G
  G --> H[URL state persists tab, eventType, actorId, dateFrom, dateTo]
  H --> I[Reload history slice from canonical history query params]
  I --> J{historyPageInfo.has_more}
  J -->|Yes| K[Load more appends next cursor page]
  J -->|No| L[History list remains complete]
  E --> M[Telemetry state resolves to ready, empty, degraded, or restricted]
  F --> M
